ver:border-blue-500/20 hover:bg-slate-50/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900/30 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors\">Sub-500ms Cloud Sync</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">Progressive background updates. Automatically sync states and exam answers asynchronously.</p></div><div class=\"group relative flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-850 hover:border-blue-500/30 dark:hover:border-blue-500/20 hover:bg-slate-50/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900/30 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-smartphone\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"20\" x=\"5\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors\">Offline State Recovery</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">Save quiz progress locally if connection drops and sync automatically once back online.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full py-16 lg:py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/10 border-t border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-900/50\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-3 mb-16\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-rose-500 uppercase\">Common Questions</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white\">General App FAQ Preview</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">Need help? Here are some quick answers to guide you. For a comprehensive list, visit our full FAQ page.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-850 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/60 p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-help text-rose-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-snug\">How do I create a student account?</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed pl-7\">Download the student app from the Google Play Store, click &#x27;Register&#x27;, and enter your mobile number. A registration request will be sent to the administrator. Once approved, you can log in.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-850 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/60 p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-help text-rose-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-snug\">What happens if my internet connection drops during an exam?</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed pl-7\">MathsWithSD saves your answers locally in a secure offline cache. You can continue taking your test. Once internet is restored, the progress automatically syncs to the server.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-850 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/60 p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-help text-rose-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-snug\">How are my test scores and metrics calculated?</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed pl-7\">Scores are evaluated using standard canonical formulas: overall accuracy (based on total test questions), attempted accuracy (correct answers over attempted questions), and attempt rate.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-850 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/60 p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-help text-rose-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-snug\">Why can&#x27;t I immediately see my exam results?</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed pl-7\">If the test is scheduled for a specific time window, scores remain hidden until the exam time officially closes to prevent answers from being shared between students.</p></div></div><div class=\"text-center mt-10\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/faq\"><span>View all 30+ FAQs</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full py-16 lg:py-20 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-indigo-700 to-rose-500 text-white\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/10 pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight\">Ready to Accelerate Your Mathematics Learning?</h2><p class=\"text-base